hh3cEvb.name: hh3cEvb
hh3cEvb.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Haidian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cEvb.description: EVB management information base for managing devices that support Ethernet Virtual Bridging. This MIB is an extension of IEEE8021-EVB-MIB.

hh3cEvbSetResult.name: hh3cEvbSetResult
hh3cEvbSetResult.description: If a set operation on EVB-MIB-tables returns success, this object indicates the actual result of this operation. Otherwise, it is meaningless. unknown: The set operation on the node has been completed, but the result could only be got from the table which the set operation happended. processing: The set operation is in process. Another set operation cannot be performed at this time. success: The set operation has succeeded. failed: The set operation has failed.

hh3cEvbDefaultManagerTable.name: hh3cEvbDefaultManagerTable
hh3cEvbDefaultManagerTable.description: A table that contains configuration information for the default Virtual Station Interface (VSI) manager.

hh3cEvbDefaultManagerEntry.name: hh3cEvbDefaultManagerEntry
hh3cEvbDefaultManagerEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for the default VSI manager.

hh3cEvbManagerIndex.name: hh3cEvbManagerIndex
hh3cEvbManagerIndex.description: Index of the default manager table.

hh3cEvbManagerType.name: hh3cEvbManagerType
hh3cEvbManagerType.description: Type of the default VSI manager. ipv4: Specifies the IPv4 address of the default VSI manager. ipv6: Specifies the IPv6 address of the default VSI manager. name: Specifies the name of the default VSI manager, a case-insensitive string of 1 to 127 characters. local: Specifies the device as the default VSI manager.

hh3cEvbManagerID.name: hh3cEvbManagerID
hh3cEvbManagerID.description: Default VSI manager. The value is zero-length string when the VSI manager type is 'local'.

hh3cEvbManagerPort.name: hh3cEvbManagerPort
hh3cEvbManagerPort.description: Port number of the default VSI manager. Optional when the VSI manager type is not 'local'. If the VSI manager type is 'local', it returns zero.

hh3cEvbManagerRowStatus.name: hh3cEvbManagerRowStatus
hh3cEvbManagerRowStatus.description: Row status: CreateAndGo, Active, or Destroy.

hh3cEvbPortConfigTable.name: hh3cEvbPortConfigTable
hh3cEvbPortConfigTable.description: A table that contains configuration information for the EVB bridge port.

hh3cEvbPortConfigEntry.name: hh3cEvbPortConfigEntry
hh3cEvbPortConfigEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for the EVB bridge port.

hh3cEvbSchannelConfigTable.name: hh3cEvbSchannelConfigTable
hh3cEvbSchannelConfigTable.description: A table that contains configuration information for the S-channel.

hh3cEvbSchannelConfigEntry.name: hh3cEvbSchannelConfigEntry
hh3cEvbSchannelConfigEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for the S-channel.

hh3cEvbSchannelSVLAN.name: hh3cEvbSchannelSVLAN
hh3cEvbSchannelSVLAN.description: S-VLAN ID. 0 means that the S-channel is not bound to any S-VLAN. 1 represents the SVID for the default S-channel S-channel 1.

hh3cEvbMacLearningStatus.name: hh3cEvbMacLearningStatus
hh3cEvbMacLearningStatus.description: The MAC address learning function is enabled or not.

hh3cEvbRRStatus.name: hh3cEvbRRStatus
hh3cEvbRRStatus.description: The RR mode for the S-channel is enabled or not.

hh3cEvbSchannelRowStatus.name: hh3cEvbSchannelRowStatus
hh3cEvbSchannelRowStatus.description: Row status: CreateAndGo, Active, or Destroy.

hh3cEvbVSIConfigTable.name: hh3cEvbVSIConfigTable
hh3cEvbVSIConfigTable.description: A table that contains configuration information for the VSI.

hh3cEvbVSIConfigEntry.name: hh3cEvbVSIConfigEntry
hh3cEvbVSIConfigEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for the VSI.

hh3cEvbSBPPortNumber.name: hh3cEvbSBPPortNumber
hh3cEvbSBPPortNumber.description: The Station-facing Bridge Port (SBP) port number.

hh3cEvbVSICommand.name: hh3cEvbVSICommand
hh3cEvbVSICommand.description: This object indicates the association or pre-associate property of the VSI.

hh3cEvbVSIIsActive.name: hh3cEvbVSIIsActive
hh3cEvbVSIIsActive.description: The VSI is activated or not. Activate a VSI after configuring a VSI filter, and deactivate a VSI before removing a VSI filter.

hh3cEvbVSIRowStatus.name: hh3cEvbVSIRowStatus
hh3cEvbVSIRowStatus.description: Row status: CreateAndGo, Active, or Destroy.

hh3cEvbVSIFilterConfigTable.name: hh3cEvbVSIFilterConfigTable
hh3cEvbVSIFilterConfigTable.description: A table that contains configuration information for filters of the VSI.

hh3cEvbVSIFilterConfigEntry.name: hh3cEvbVSIFilterConfigEntry
hh3cEvbVSIFilterConfigEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for filters of the VSI.

hh3cEvbVSIMac.name: hh3cEvbVSIMac
hh3cEvbVSIMac.description: The MAC address part of the MAC/VLANs for a VSI.

hh3cEvbVSIVlanId.name: hh3cEvbVSIVlanId
hh3cEvbVSIVlanId.description: The VLAN ID part of the MAC/VLANs for a VSI.

hh3cEvbVSIFilterRowStatus.name: hh3cEvbVSIFilterRowStatus
hh3cEvbVSIFilterRowStatus.description: Row status: CreateAndGo, Active, or Destroy.

hh3cFlex10PortConfigTable.name: hh3cFlex10PortConfigTable
hh3cFlex10PortConfigTable.description: A table that contains configuration information for the flex10 bridge port.

hh3cFlex10PortConfigEntry.name: hh3cFlex10PortConfigEntry
hh3cFlex10PortConfigEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for the flex10 bridge port.

hh3cFlex10PortEnableStatus.name: hh3cFlex10PortEnableStatus
hh3cFlex10PortEnableStatus.description: The flex10 function is enabled or not.

hh3cFlex10RemoteSchannelTable.name: hh3cFlex10RemoteSchannelTable
hh3cFlex10RemoteSchannelTable.description: A table that contains remote S-channel details.

hh3cFlex10RemoteSchannelEntry.name: hh3cFlex10RemoteSchannelEntry
hh3cFlex10RemoteSchannelEntry.description: A list of objects describing remote S-channels.

hh3cFlex10RemSchDesFormat.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchDesFormat
hh3cFlex10RemSchDesFormat.description: Description format of the remote S-channel.

hh3cFlex10RemSchTerminationType.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchTerminationType
hh3cFlex10RemSchTerminationType.description: Termination type of the remote S-channel. 0: PCI Physical Function (Primary). 1: SRIOV Virtual Function. 2: PCI Physical Function (Secondary). 3: Virtual Switch Port. 4: NCSI Port. 2147483647: This value means a Description TLV with format 0 has not been received. other: Unknown termination type.

hh3cFlex10RemSchTerminationCap.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchTerminationCap
hh3cFlex10RemSchTerminationCap.description: Termination capabilities of the remote S-channel. If a Description TLV with format 0 has not been received, it returns all zeros.

hh3cFlex10RemSchTrafficClass.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchTrafficClass
hh3cFlex10RemSchTrafficClass.description: Traffic classes of the remote S-channel. If a Description TLV with format 0 has not been received, it returns all zeros.

hh3cFlex10RemSchCir.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchCir
hh3cFlex10RemSchCir.description: Committed Information Rate (CIR) of the remote S-channel. If a Description TLV with format 0 has not been received, it returns 0.

hh3cFlex10RemSchPir.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchPir
hh3cFlex10RemSchPir.description: Peak Information Rate (PIR) of the remote S-channel. If a Description TLV with format 0 has not been received, it returns 0.

hh3cFlex10RemSchConnectionID.name: hh3cFlex10RemSchConnectionID
hh3cFlex10RemSchConnectionID.description: Connection instance ID of the remote S-channel. The value is a zero-length string if a Description TLV with format 1 has not been received. Otherwise it returns a string with length 16.

hh3cFlex10SchannelLinkCtlTable.name: hh3cFlex10SchannelLinkCtlTable
hh3cFlex10SchannelLinkCtlTable.description: A table that contains link status information for the S-channel.

hh3cFlex10SchannelLinkCtlEntry.name: hh3cFlex10SchannelLinkCtlEntry
hh3cFlex10SchannelLinkCtlEntry.description: A list of objects containing information for the S-channel.

hh3cFlex10SchannelLocalStatus.name: hh3cFlex10SchannelLocalStatus
hh3cFlex10SchannelLocalStatus.description: Link status of the local S-channel.

hh3cFlex10SchannelRemoteStatus.name: hh3cFlex10SchannelRemoteStatus
hh3cFlex10SchannelRemoteStatus.description: Link status of the remote S-channel.
